              Lets Start the journey withh us
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-6">
            <p class="text-white mt-5 pt-4">
              Created by
              <span class="text-footer"> Kelompok 3 KKP MSIB BATCH 4</span> |
              Copyright &copy;2024
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>


